<h3>Implementation Notes</h3>
<ul>
  <li>ViewEngine is a utility class, not a registered block &mdash; imported by blocks that need it</li>
  <li>ViewBehavior extends <code>CustomAttribute</code> (from Web Behaviors)</li>
  <li>ViewShowBehavior extends <code>CustomAttribute</code> (from Web Behaviors)</li>
  <li>ViewIfDirective and ViewSwitchDirective extend <code>CustomTemplateDirective</code> (from Web Directives)</li>
  <li>Directives use comment-based markers for template boundaries (like ForEach)</li>
  <li>ViewBehavior listens for <code>command</code> events from Invoker Commands API</li>
  <li>ViewBehavior falls back to click handlers for browsers without Invoker Commands</li>
  <li>All blocks delegate hidden mode, events, transitions, and exclusive groups to ViewEngine</li>
</ul>

<h3>Exports</h3>
<table>
  <tr><th>Export</th><th>Description</th></tr>
  <tr><td><code>ViewEngine</code></td><td>Shared core: hidden modes, toggle events, transitions, exclusive groups</td></tr>
  <tr><td><code>ViewBehavior</code></td><td>Behavior: imperative show/hide via Invoker Commands</td></tr>
  <tr><td><code>ViewShowBehavior</code></td><td>Behavior: expression-bound reactive visibility</td></tr>
  <tr><td><code>ViewIfDirective</code></td><td>Directive: structural if/else conditional rendering</td></tr>
  <tr><td><code>ViewSwitchDirective</code></td><td>Directive: structural multi-branch rendering</td></tr>
  <tr><td><code>ViewEngineOptions</code></td><td>Configuration type for hidden mode, transition, group name</td></tr>
</table>
